'''Estonia''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in March 2019. Its default cities are only the capital, Tallinn.

Estonia was part of a March 2019 [[Updates|update]] that added 8 new countries into the game. The other 7 were [[Portugal]], [[Norway]], [[Indonesia]], [[Denmark]], [[Finland]], [[Romania]], and [[Singapore]]. This update was also the update that brought [[Pets]] for the first time. This update was also the first to have multiple new countries being added other than the ones originally released.

Estonia has a low tax rate, and no inheritance tax however, it doesn't have free healthcare or free universities. 

